            "image_pc": "shopify://shop_images/publicdomainq-0083387fmz.jpg",
            "image_sp": "shopify://shop_images/publicdomainq-0083387fmz.jpg",
            "textarea": "\"I’ve been starting my day with AG1 for over 8 years—it’s been a non-negotiable in my routine. Now with AGZ, I’ve finally got the other half covered. This day-to-night combo makes full-body support effortless with everything I need to perform, optimize rest, and show up ready again tomorrow.”"
